WEBVTT

00:01.360 --> 00:02.760
Your son is not coercing Father

00:03.120 --> 00:04.320
All your son's thoughts

00:04.560 --> 00:05.920
Are for Great Xuan's state

00:06.680 --> 00:07.360
Throughout history

00:07.600 --> 00:08.600
Loyalty and filial piety are one

00:09.000 --> 00:09.800
To serve the sovereign without loyalty

00:10.040 --> 00:10.840
Is also unfilial

00:17.000 --> 00:19.040
You haven't been to the palace in a while

00:20.440 --> 00:21.120
Accompany me

00:21.320 --> 00:22.360
For a game of chess

00:23.760 --> 00:24.800
Yes, Father
